&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; margin-top: 0pt;&quot;&gt;i&#39;m having a hard time
understanding your explanation. can you please post two examples, one
&quot;RPC plus streaming&quot;, the other true REST? &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; margin-top: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
